Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:21.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善々悪々も審議不能になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:25.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全部嫌になった　それさえも幸せな結末だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だめだ　そんな悲しいこと言うな　まだ世界は生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}君が泣いてたって生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だからこの空の先を見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:40.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}邪魔すぎる運命のターゲット睨みながら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:44.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,800)\blur2\be1}言えそうで良かった「まだ愛していたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:36.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}为错位的焦点所惑 四下寻找说辞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}看吧枯叶起舞 终会化为蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:40.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}然后调节到位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:42.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,0)\blur2\be1}然后是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}时过境迁太急 秒速开始不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:48.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全因自己武断的选择开端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:51.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以必须做出了断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:54.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无聊的理由 是停止思考的铁证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}无法守护应守护之物 那就不要乱出头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:02.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共鸣 荣光 称赞 都不应奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:06.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不明真相的引力 将常识归于虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:08.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}会扣下扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不是开玩笑的 幻觉已经开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:15.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}充满谎言的海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:18.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}让心都变得模糊的海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:21.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善善恶恶都无法评议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:25.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全都变得讨厌 连这都是幸福的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不行 不要说得如此悲凉 世界依然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}即使你会哭泣也还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以想看到这片天空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:40.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}一边瞪视过于碍眼的命运的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:44.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,800)\blur2\be1}能说出口就好 “还想继续爱”
